---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';

const title = 'Disclaimer';
const description = 'Disclaimer for Yasir Aljiyadi website';
---

<Base title={title} description={description} lang="en">
  <article class="prose">
    <h1>Disclaimer</h1>

    <p class="intro">
      The content published on this website is for educational and informational purposes only.
    </p>

    <h2>Nature of Content</h2>
    <p>
      The articles and information provided on this website reflect personal opinions and experiences in the field of human resources and management. This content:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Is not official legal or professional advice</li>
      <li>May change over time and circumstances</li>
      <li>Should be verified before making important decisions</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Legal and Regulatory Information</h2>
    <p>
      When discussing laws or regulations (such as Saudi Labor Law or Social Insurance):
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Information may change with system updates</li>
      <li>Refer to official authorities for accurate information</li>
      <li>Consult a lawyer or specialist for important legal matters</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
    <p>
      We make every effort to provide accurate and useful information, but we are not responsible for:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Any errors or omissions in the information</li>
      <li>Decisions made based on the content</li>
      <li>Consequences resulting from applying the information</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Use of Information</h2>
    <p>
      By using this website, you agree that:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Content is for educational and general knowledge only</li>
      <li>You take full responsibility for any decisions you make</li>
      <li>You will consult specialists before making important decisions</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Updates</h2>
    <p>
      We strive to update content regularly, but some information may become outdated. Always check the article's publication date.
    </p>

    <p class="update-date">
      Last updated: April 2026
    </p>
  </article>
</Base>

<style>
  .prose {
    max-width: 65ch;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
  }

  .intro {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--gray-600);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--gray-900);
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--gray-800);
  }

  p, li {
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--gray-700);
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
  }

  ul {
    margin: 1rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  li {
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
  }

  .update-date {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--gray-500);
    font-style: italic;
  }
</style>
